    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with normal use. Inside, the cabin is in great shape with minimal wear on the upholstery and all electronic features functioning as intended. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, providing a comfortable and dependable driving experience.",
      "price": 32000.0,
